  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/dd7b2c293207b41d95146004552a5d53.poster.avif?t=1734820918\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/dd7b2c293207b41d95146004552a5d53.webm?t=1734820918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/dd7b2c293207b41d95146004552a5d53.mp4?t=1734820918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >My reaper rise! My reaper rage!</h2><br><br>In a world ravaged by wars, death and agony, where kingdoms have fallen and cities were burned to ashes. In the aftermath of the Great War, the Mortal races struggle to rebuild what was lost and reshape what was destroyed.<br><br>Amidst the chaos, in the depths of agony and despair, bones were forged, and by the Eternal Flames they were ignited. A deathless and hollow reaper emerged from the fire.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/3179178671bbacd66109675c13495062.poster.avif?t=1734820918\" width=600 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/3179178671bbacd66109675c13495062.webm?t=1734820918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/3179178671bbacd66109675c13495062.mp4?t=1734820918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>All forms of life rejected him, even the dead, as if the world itself was fighting him, the reaper had no choice but to proceed forward and no one will stop him, that until he finds the ultimate truth.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/d71b04797100a2ce8893140be5c5da6b.poster.avif?t=1734820918\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/d71b04797100a2ce8893140be5c5da6b.webm?t=1734820918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/d71b04797100a2ce8893140be5c5da6b.mp4?t=1734820918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight your way through hordes of enemies.<br>Reap everything that stands in your way.</h2><br><br>Reaper of Immortals is a Pixel-art Platformer Adventure game, with a rich lore and world building, it tells the story of a lost reaper who is seeking his true purpose.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/9ca4d521973f41f87b5dcc26e6f80772.poster.avif?t=1734820918\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/9ca4d521973f41f87b5dcc26e6f80772.webm?t=1734820918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/9ca4d521973f41f87b5dcc26e6f80772.mp4?t=1734820918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game is about 5 hours long, with 4 world settings across 2 continents.<br>All the levels can be replayed in order to look for hidden chests, missed dialogues, secret paths, different play-styles and Steam Achievements.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/233bd46f1649783b6524ee666fc7d30a.poster.avif?t=1734820918\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/233bd46f1649783b6524ee666fc7d30a.webm?t=1734820918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/233bd46f1649783b6524ee666fc7d30a.mp4?t=1734820918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A Thrilling adventure with unique characters and story telling.<br></li><li>4 locations with beautiful atmosphere.<br></li><li>16 challenging levels.<br></li><li>9 boss battles with different mechanics.<br></li><li>20 plus types of enemies.<br></li><li>Full Controller support.<br></li><li>Game stats and Achievements. <br></li><li>Ultrawide 21:9 support.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/dd7b2c293207b41d95146004552a5d53.poster.avif?t=1734820918\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/dd7b2c293207b41d95146004552a5d53.webm?t=1734820918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/dd7b2c293207b41d95146004552a5d53.mp4?t=1734820918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This game was created by a single person who put his heart and soul into making it, and with very little means.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/dd7b2c293207b41d95146004552a5d53.poster.avif?t=1734820918\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/dd7b2c293207b41d95146004552a5d53.webm?t=1734820918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/dd7b2c293207b41d95146004552a5d53.mp4?t=1734820918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >My reaper rise! My reaper rage!</h2><br><br>In a world ravaged by wars, death and agony, where kingdoms have fallen and cities were burned to ashes. In the aftermath of the Great War, the Mortal races struggle to rebuild what was lost and reshape what was destroyed.<br><br>Amidst the chaos, in the depths of agony and despair, bones were forged, and by the Eternal Flames they were ignited. A deathless and hollow reaper emerged from the fire.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/3179178671bbacd66109675c13495062.poster.avif?t=1734820918\" width=600 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/3179178671bbacd66109675c13495062.webm?t=1734820918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1981020/extras/3179178671bbacd66109675c13495062.mp4?t=1734820918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>All forms of life rejected him, even the dead, as if the world itself was fighting him, the reaper had no choice but to proceed forward and no one will stop him, that until he finds the ultimate truth.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\"